                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17960914-84-off465 t17960914-84-cd466"></join>, a hempen bags value 4d. a saw, value 2s. a dovetail saw, value 1s. 6d. a jack plane, value 14d. a smoothing plane, value 15d. a rabbit plane, value 6d. two mallers, value 6d. two gimblets, value 4d. one gouge, value 6d. one axe, value 6d. three broad awls, value 3d. four chissels, value 12d. a Turkey oil stone, value 6d. an iron hammer, value 4d. and an augur, value 4d.
